  line `by a Collective Investment`
  line `Management Company registered`
  line `with the Securities and Exchange`
  line `Board of India under the Securities`
  line `and Exchange Board o f India`
  line `(Collective Investment Scheme)`
  line `Regulations, 1999.`
  line `( ii ) Any scheme or an arrangement`
  line `registered with the Securities and`
  line `Exchange Board of India under the`
  line `Securities and Exchange Board of`
  line `India (Alternative Investment`
  line `Funds) Regulations, 2012.`
  line `( iii ) Any scheme or an`
  line `arrangement, pursuant to which`
  line `funds are managed by a portfolio`
  line `manager, registered under the`
  line `Securities and Exchange Board of`
  line `India (Portfolio Managers)`
  line `Regulations, 1993.`
  line `( iv ) Any scheme or an arrangement`
  line `regulated under the Securities and`
  line `Exchange Board of India (Share`
  line `Based Employee Benefits)`
  line `Regulations, 2014 or providing for`
  line `employee benefits as permitted`
  line `under the Companies Act, 2013 (18`
  line `of 2013).`
  line `( v ) Any other scheme or an`
  line `arrangement registered under the`
  line `Securities a nd Exchange Board of`
  line `India Act, 1992 (15 of 1992), or the`
  line `regulations made thereunder.`
