obj_root_law_sections_23_content:
  string
  line 23
  line `THE SECOND SCHEDULE`
  line `( See section 4 2)`
  line `A MENDMENTS TO CERTAIN ENACTMENTS`
  line `PART I`
  line `A MENDMENT TO THE R ESERVE B ANK OF I NDIA`
  line `ACT, 1934`
  line `Amendment of section 45 - I of Act 2 of 1934.In the Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934, in`
  line `section 45 - I, in clause ( bb ), after Explanation II, the followi ng Explanation shall be inserted, namely: —`
  line `“ Explanation III. — The amounts accepted by a co - operative society from the members or shareholders,`
  line `by whatever name called, but excluding the amounts received as share capital, shall be deemed to be`
  line `deposits for the purposes of this clause, if such members or sharehol ders are nominal or associate`
  line `members, by whatever name called, who do not have full voting rights in the meetings of such co -`
  line `operative society. ”.`
  line `PART II`
  line `A MENDMENTS TO THE S ECURITIES AND E XCHANGE B OARD OF I NDIA ACT, 1992`
  line `In the Securities and Exchange Board of India Act, 1992, —`
  line `Amendment of section 11 of Act 15 of 1992. — ( i ) in section 11, in sub - section ( 4 ), for`
  line `clause ( e ), the following clause shall be substituted, namely: —`
  line `“ ( e ) attach, for a period not exceeding ninety days, ba nk accounts or other property of any`
  line `intermediary or any person associated with the securities market in any manner involved in violation of`
  line `any of the provisions of this Act, or the rules or the regulations made thereunder:`
  line `Provided that the Board shall, within ninety days of the said attachment, obtain confirmation of the`
  line `said attachment from the Special Court, established under section 26A, having jurisdiction and on such`
  line `confirmation, such attachment shall continue during the pendency of the aforesaid p roceedings and on`
  line `conclusion of the said proceedings, the provisions of section 28A shall apply:`
  line `Provided further that only property, bank account or accounts or any transaction entered therein, so far`
  line `as it relates to the proceeds actually involved in vio lation of any of the provisions of this Act, or the rules`
  line `or the regulations made thereunder shall be allowed to be attached. ”;`
  line `( ii ) in section 28A, after Explanation 3, the following Explanation shall be inserted, namely: —`
  line `“ Explanation 4. — The interest referred to in section 220 of the Income - tax Act, 1961 shall`
  line `commence from the date the amount became payable by the person. ”.`
obj_root_law_sections_23_footnotes:
  string
  line
