obj_root_law_sections_24_content:
  string
  line 24
  line `PART III`
  line `A MENDMENT TO THE M ULTI - S TATE C O - OPERATIVE S OCIETIES A CT, 2002`
  line `Amendment of section 67 of Act 39 of 2 002. — In the Multi - State Co - operative Societies Act, 2002, in`
  line `section 67, in sub - section (1), —`
  line `( a ) after the words “ receive deposits ”, the words “ from its voting members ” shall be inserted;`
  line `( b ) the following Explanation shall be inserted, namely: —`
  line `“ Explana tion. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby clarified that a multi - State co - operative society`
  line `shall not be entitled to receive deposits from persons other than voting members. ”.`
  line _______
obj_root_law_sections_24_footnotes:
  string
  line
